{
  "stem": "18056.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had-- we had a-- an American chaplain married us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was quite-- quite an-- an occasion in Bremen for our wedding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very, very, important occasion in Bremen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a big question for myself, too, at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know whether I should or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my wife Ursula didn't want to stay in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she-- so I guess she put a little pressure on me that we should leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I left this business with a good manager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a very good manager.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- we left it there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We left the business, and-- and we came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very-- actually, I did not have a very complicated immigration problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in Bremen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bremen didn't have that many refugees as, let's say, Munich or other cities had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and explaining to the counselor that, in a way, I-- I don't-- I want to make a living.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to live in a free country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I want to have all the good things that are in a-- in a free country like America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I guess he bought it, in a way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, my wife, being born in Germany, that [INAUDIBLE] was better than the Polish [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had the Polish boarder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had the German boarder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they took that into consideration, and that helped us go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By boat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came with the And the was one of the troop ships that brought the troops to-- to Europe and back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was an American ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came-- with that ship we came to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah, about 900 or 600.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a tough trip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in January, very, very rough trip.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
